name: Orbital Oops
description:
** SORRY NO MOBILE SUPPORT **

CONTROLS: Spacebar, A & D

Orbital Oops is a thrilling and challenging rocket landing game. Players take control of a spacecraft and attempt to land it safely on a rocky, uneven planet surface. With each successful landing, players earn points, but if they land too fast, the rocket will explode. The objective of the game is to get the highest score possible, but watch out for those tricky landing spots! Can you master the art of planetary landing and achieve the ultimate high score? Download Orbital Oops now and find out!
